%html
  %head
    %meta{charset: "utf8"}
    %meta{name: "viewport", content:"width=device-width"}
    %meta{name: "google-site-verification", content:"3Ccn3zKixsjitl3gKva3cQS3hpFJdXbJAHZ411OuUSg"}

    %link{rel: "stylesheet", media: "screen", href: "./css/v2/application.css"}
    %link{rel: "stylesheet", media: "screen", href: "./css/magnific-popup.css"}
    %script{src: "./js/jquery.min.js"}
    %script{src: "./js/jquery.nav.js"}
    
    %script{src: "./js/foundation.min.js"}
    %script{src: "./js/foundation.equalizer.js"}
    %title
      Sean Iams - Product Designer

  %body.v2
    .fixed
      %nav{id: "nav", "data-topbar" => "", role: "navigation"}
        .row
          .small-0.medium-2.spacer.columns
            %a.avatar{href: "/"}
              %img{src: "../images/profile-photo-right.png", width: "110", height: "110"}
          .small-12.medium-8.columns
            %center
              %ul
                %li
                  %a{href: "#recent-work"}
                    RECENT WORK
                %li
                  %a{href: "#my-process"}
                    MY PROCESS
                %li
                  %a{href: "#about-me"}
                    ABOUT ME
          .small-0.medium-2.spacer.columns

    .home
      .row.intro
        .small-12.columns
          %h1
            Hello! I'm Sean.
          %p
            I'm a product designer based in San Francisco creating software that empowers people do the best work of their lives.
      .row.divider.recent-projects
        %a.nav-anchor{id: "recent-work"}
        .icon
          %img{src: "../images/briefcase.png", width: "150", height: "150"}
        %h2
          Recent Work
        %p
          Iâ€™ve enjoyed creating world class software with clients and companies of all shapes and sizes. Recent projects run the gamut from research, design & prototyping, to front-end implementation.
      .row.section
        .small-12.columns
          .row.project

            .small-12.columns
              .row.logo
                .small-12.columns
                  .logo-container
                    %img{src: "../images/citrine-logo-209.png", width: "209", height: "101"}
              .row.description
                .small-12.medium-8.columns.project-blurb
                  %h3
                    Visual & Interaction Design, Usability Testing
                  %p
                    Citrine, an advanced materials analytics platform, wanted to increase user-uploads. Through user testing, we discovered what was preventing users from signing up and uploading. Our efforts resulted in redesigning key screens and implementing enhancements to the onboarding process.
                  %p
                    %a.button{href: "/citrine.html"}
                      Read more.
                .small-12.medium-4.columns.project-icons
                  %ul.project-icons
                    %li
                      .icon
                        %img{src: "../images/cropping.png", width: "31", height: "31"}
                      .caption
                        visual & interaction design
                    %li
                      .icon
                        %img{src: "../images/eye.png", width: "47", height: "31"}
                      .caption
                        usability testing
                    %li
                      .icon
                        %img{src: "../images/markup-brackets.png", width: "41", height: "31"}
                      .caption
                        front-end development

          .row.project
            .small-12.columns
              .row.logo
                .small-12.columns
                  .logo-container
                    %img{src: "../images/urx-logo.svg", width: "265", height: "100"}
              .row.description
                .small-12.medium-8.columns.project-blurb
                  %h3
                    Interaction Design & Mobile Prototyping
                  %p
                    URX provides developers with tools & APIs to link apps together. We performed guerrilla usability testing and then used that behavioral insight to recommend design improvements to drive engagement.
                .small-12.medium-4.columns.project-icons
                  %ul.project-icons
                    %li
                      .icon
                        %img{src: "../images/cropping.png", width: "31", height: "31"}
                      .caption
                        interaction design
                    %li
                      .icon
                        %img{src: "../images/mobile-device.png", width: "20", height: "32"}
                      .caption
                        mobile prototyping
                    %li
                      .icon
                        %img{src: "../images/eye.png", width: "47", height: "31"}
                      .caption
                        behavioral testing

          .row.project.last
            .small-12.columns
              .row.logo
                .small-12.columns
                  .logo-container
                    %img{src: "../images/nb-logo-348.png", width: "348", height: "100"}
              .row.description
                .small-12.medium-8.columns.project-blurb
                  %h3
                    User Research & Persona Development
                  %p
                    Noble Brewer wanted a more complete customer personality profile to guide design decisions and product direction. Our team built fully-researched and validated personas for Noble Brewer. They were able to use this insight to orient their marketing and product development efforts to the needs and goals of real people.
                .small-12.medium-4.columns.project-icons
                  %ul.project-icons
                    %li
                      .icon
                        %img{src: "../images/convo-bubbles.png", width: "38", height: "31"}
                      .caption
                        user interviews
                    %li
                      .icon
                        %img{src: "../images/bullet-points.png", width: "32", height: "32"}
                      .caption
                        surveys & screeners
                    %li
                      .icon
                        %img{src: "../images/personas.png", width: "25", height: "31"}
                      .caption
                        persona development

      .row.divider.my-process
        %a.nav-anchor{id: "my-process"}
        .icon
          %img{src: "../images/my-process.png", width: "150", height: "150"}
        %h2
          My Process
        %p
          I work with end-users and co-workers in an agile process iterating through research, design, and development.
      .row.section.process
        .small-12.medium-4.columns
          .process-step
            .icon-container
              .icon
                %img{src: "../images/convo-bubbles.png", width: "38", height: "31"}
            %h3
              Research & Test
            %ul
              %li
                user interviews
              %li
                user-testing prototypes
              %li
                site & app analytics
        .small-12.medium-4.columns
          .process-step
            .icon-container
              .icon
                %img{src: "../images/diamond.png", width: "41", height: "40"}
            %h3
              Design & Prototype
            %ul
              %li
                interactive prototypes
              %li
                wireframes
              %li
                collaborative design sprints
        .small-12.medium-4.columns
          .process-step
            .icon-container
              .icon
                %img{src: "../images/browser-code.png", width: "35", height: "31"}
            %h3
              Build & Deploy
            %ul
              %li
                html + css
              %li
                javascript
              %li
                angular, backbone, react
      .row.divider.about-me
        %a.nav-anchor{id: "about-me"}
        .icon
          %img{src: "../images/about-me.png", width: "150", height: "150"}
        .small-12.columns
          %h2
            About Me
        .small-12.columns
          %p
            Professionally, I enjoy digital product design and front-end development. For fun, I enjoy sports involving the ocean, skies, and mountains.
      .row.section.about-me
        .small-12.medium-8.columns.about-me
          .blurb
            %h3
              Professionally
            %p
              With 10 years of experience as a full-stack software engineer at companies like Groupon, Rise, and Obtiva, I'm now enjoying the design side of things. I love the process of research, interaction design, and prototyping to find the most practical and elegant solution. The right solutions are out there, and it's my job as a designer to work with users and stakeholders to find them and refine them.
          .blurb
            %h3
              For Fun
            %p
              I love aviation and adventure sports. I've steadily added pilot ratings to my logbook over the years, and I also enjoy surfing, snowboarding, and kiteboarding.
        .small-12.medium-4.columns.big-icons
          .icon
            %img{src: "../images/book.png", width: "65", height: "57"}
          .icon
            %img{src: "../images/airplane.png", width: "65", height: "65"}
          .icon
            %img{src: "../images/surfboard.png", width: "65", height: "65"}

    .footer
      .row
        .small-12.medium-6.columns
          .row
            .contact-form
              .row
                .small-12.columns
                  %h3
                    Send me a lovely message.

              %form{action: "//formspree.io/smiamsdemo@gmail.com", method: "POST"}
                .row
                  .small-12.columns
                    %label{name: "_replyto"}
                      Your e-mail address:
                      %input{type: "email", class: "text email", name: "_replyto"}
                .row
                  .small-12.columns
                    %label
                      Your flowery prose:
                      %textarea{class: "input-group-field", name: "message", rows: "4"}
                .row
                  .small-12.columns
                    %input{type: "submit", value: "Send", class: "button"}
        .small-12.medium-6.columns
          %ul.footer-links
            %li
              %a{href: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/seaniams", target: "_blank"}
                LinkedIn profile.
            %li
              %a{href: "/resume.pdf", target: "_blank"}
                Resume.

